llege. But the numbers are compelling. </p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Despite a rise in foss=
il fuel usage this year, the IEA believes we are near the peak of global fo=
ssil fuel usage and embarking on a long, slow, but necessary course towards=
